Goodyear to Raise Truck Tire Prices 15%, Modern Tire Reports

-- B y   C r a i g   T r u d e l l
-- 
2011-03-21T20:07:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/goodyear-to-raise-truck-tire-prices-15-modern-tire-reports.html
Goodyear Tire & Rubber Co. (GT)  will
increase prices on its commercial truck tires by as much as 15
percent starting next month, Modern Tire Dealer reported today.  The company also will boost the price of tread rubber by as
much as 7 percent, the publication reported on its  website ,
citing a Goodyear spokesman it didnâ€™t identify. The spokesman
said reasons for the increases included rising prices for raw
materials, Modern Tire Dealer said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
